---
import BrandBookLayout from '../../layouts/BrandBookLayout.astro';
---

<BrandBookLayout
  title="Brand Book"
  description="The Trenches design system and brand guidelines"
>
  <div class="brand-overview">
    <header class="brand-header">
      <div class="brand-header__badge">Design System</div>
      <h1 class="brand-header__title">The <em>Trenches</em></h1>
      <p class="brand-header__tagline">Practical engineering insights from the frontlines</p>
    </header>

    <section class="brand-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">Core Values</span>
        <h2>Brand Identity</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-intro">
        The Trenches is a technical blog focused on data engineering, infrastructure economics,
        and system design. The brand voice is candid, data-driven, pragmatic, and technically rigorous.
      </p>

      <div class="brand-values">
        <div class="brand-value">
          <div class="brand-value__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 20h9"></path>
              <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4Z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Candid</h3>
          <p>Direct, honest analysis without corporate fluff. We call things as we see them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-value">
          <div class="brand-value__icon brand-value__icon--cool">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="20" y2="10"></line>
              <line x1="18" x2="18" y1="20" y2="4"></line>
              <line x1="6" x2="6" y1="20" y2="16"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven</h3>
          <p>Every claim backed by evidence. Real numbers, real case studies, real results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-value">
          <div class="brand-value__icon brand-value__icon--violet">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12.22 2h-.44a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v.18a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.73l-.43.25a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 0-2.73.73l-.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 .73 2.73l.15.1a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.72v.51a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.74l-.15.09a2 2 0 0 0-.73 2.73l.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 2.73.73l.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.43.25a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.73V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h.44a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-.18a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.73l.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.15.08a2 2 0 0 0 2.73-.73l.22-.39a2 2 0 0 0-.73-2.73l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.74v-.5a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.74l.15-.09a2 2 0 0 0 .73-2.73l-.22-.38a2 2 0 0 0-2.73-.73l-.15.08a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.73V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Pragmatic</h3>
          <p>Solutions that work in the real world. No ivory tower architectures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-value">
          <div class="brand-value__icon brand-value__icon--rose">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
              <path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Rigorous</h3>
          <p>Deep technical analysis. We go beyond the surface to understand why.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="brand-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">Philosophy</span>
        <h2>Design Principles</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="design-principles">
        <div class="design-principle">
          <div class="design-principle__header">
            <span class="design-principle__number">01</span>
            <h3>Dark by Default</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            A sophisticated dark theme as the primary experience, respecting engineers' preference
            for low-light interfaces. Light theme available for accessibility and preference.
          </p>
          <div class="design-principle__visual design-principle__visual--dark">
            <div class="theme-preview theme-preview--dark"></div>
            <div class="theme-preview theme-preview--light"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="design-principle">
          <div class="design-principle__header">
            <span class="design-principle__number">02</span>
            <h3>Typography First</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Elegant serif for headlines (Playfair Display, Fraunces) paired with readable
            sans-serif for body (Inter) and precise monospace for code (JetBrains Mono).
          </p>
          <div class="design-principle__visual design-principle__visual--type">
            <span class="type-demo type-demo--display">Aa</span>
            <span class="type-demo type-demo--body">Aa</span>
            <span class="type-demo type-demo--mono">Aa</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="design-principle">
          <div class="design-principle__header">
            <span class="design-principle__number">03</span>
            <h3>Purposeful Color</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Colors serve meaning. Orange for primary actions and emphasis, secondary accents
            for visual variety, and semantic colors for clear status communication.
          </p>
          <div class="design-principle__visual design-principle__visual--color">
            <span class="color-dot color-dot--primary"></span>
            <span class="color-dot color-dot--cool"></span>
            <span class="color-dot color-dot--violet"></span>
            <span class="color-dot color-dot--rose"></span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="design-principle">
          <div class="design-principle__header">
            <span class="design-principle__number">04</span>
            <h3>Generous Space</h3>
          </div>
          <p>
            Breathing room for complex technical content. Wide margins, proper line height,
            and clear visual hierarchy to aid comprehension.
          </p>
          <div class="design-principle__visual design-principle__visual--space">
            <div class="space-demo">
              <div class="space-line"></div>
              <div class="space-line"></div>
              <div class="space-line"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="brand-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">At a Glance</span>
        <h2>Quick Reference</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-ref">
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Display Font</h4>
          <span class="quick-ref__value" style="font-family: var(--font-display)">Playfair Display</span>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Body Font</h4>
          <span class="quick-ref__value" style="font-family: var(--font-body)">Inter</span>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Code Font</h4>
          <span class="quick-ref__value" style="font-family: var(--font-mono)">JetBrains Mono</span>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Primary Accent</h4>
          <div class="quick-ref__color-row">
            <span class="quick-ref__color" style="background-color: var(--accent-primary)"></span>
            <code class="dark-value">#fb923c</code>
            <code class="light-value">#ea580c</code>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Background</h4>
          <div class="quick-ref__color-row">
            <span class="quick-ref__color" style="background-color: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border-medium)"></span>
            <code class="dark-value">#09090b</code>
            <code class="light-value">#ffffff</code>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quick-ref__item">
          <h4>Content Width</h4>
          <span class="quick-ref__value">680px</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="brand-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-header__label">Documentation</span>
        <h2>Explore the System</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="explore-links">
        <a href="/brand/colors" class="explore-link">
          <span class="explore-link__icon explore-link__icon--colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="13.5" cy="6.5" r="2.5"></circle>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="10.5" r="2.5"></circle>
              <circle cx="8.5" cy="7.5" r="2.5"></circle>
              <circle cx="6.5" cy="12.5" r="2.5"></circle>
              <path d="M12 22v-6"></path>
              <path d="M12 13a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v1a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-1a4 4 0 0 0-4-4Z"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="explore-link__content">
            <span class="explore-link__label">Colors</span>
            <span class="explore-link__description">Complete color palette and usage guidelines for both themes</span>
          </div>
          <span class="explore-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
              <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/brand/typography" class="explore-link">
          <span class="explore-link__icon explore-link__icon--typography">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="4 7 4 4 20 4 20 7"></polyline>
              <line x1="9" x2="15" y1="20" y2="20"></line>
              <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="4" y2="20"></line>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="explore-link__content">
            <span class="explore-link__label">Typography</span>
            <span class="explore-link__description">Font families, type scale, and usage examples</span>
          </div>
          <span class="explore-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
              <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/brand/components" class="explore-link">
          <span class="explore-link__icon explore-link__icon--components">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect width="7" height="7" x="3" y="3" rx="1"></rect>
              <rect width="7" height="7" x="14" y="3" rx="1"></rect>
              <rect width="7" height="7" x="14" y="14" rx="1"></rect>
              <rect width="7" height="7" x="3" y="14" rx="1"></rect>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="explore-link__content">
            <span class="explore-link__label">Components</span>
            <span class="explore-link__description">UI components, patterns, and interactive examples</span>
          </div>
          <span class="explore-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
              <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BrandBookLayout>

<style>
  .brand-overview {
    max-width: var(--wide-width);
  }

  /* Header */
  .brand-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .brand-header__badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    background-color: var(--accent-primary-muted);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .brand-header__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-6xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    line-height: var(--leading-none);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }

  .brand-header__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .brand-header__tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Section Headers */
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .section-header__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section-intro {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .brand-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  /* Brand Values */
  .brand-values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 260px), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .brand-value {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .brand-value:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .brand-value__icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background-color: var(--accent-primary-muted);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .brand-value__icon--cool {
    background-color: var(--accent-cool-muted);
    color: var(--accent-cool);
  }

  .brand-value__icon--violet {
    background-color: var(--accent-violet-muted);
    color: var(--accent-violet);
  }

  .brand-value__icon--rose {
    background-color: var(--accent-rose-muted);
    color: var(--accent-rose);
  }

  .brand-value h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .brand-value p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* Design Principles */
  .design-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 280px), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .design-principle {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .design-principle:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
  }

  .design-principle__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .design-principle__number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    background-color: var(--accent-primary-muted);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .design-principle h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .design-principle p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .design-principle__visual {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-3);
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  /* Theme Preview */
  .theme-preview {
    width: 48px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
  }

  .theme-preview--dark {
    background-color: #09090b;
  }

  .theme-preview--light {
    background-color: #ffffff;
  }

  /* Type Demo */
  .type-demo {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .type-demo--display {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .type-demo--body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .type-demo--mono {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  /* Color Dots */
  .color-dot {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  .color-dot--primary { background-color: var(--accent-primary); }
  .color-dot--cool { background-color: var(--accent-cool); }
  .color-dot--violet { background-color: var(--accent-violet); }
  .color-dot--rose { background-color: var(--accent-rose); }

  /* Space Demo */
  .space-demo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .space-line {
    height: 8px;
    background-color: var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .space-line:nth-child(1) { width: 100%; }
  .space-line:nth-child(2) { width: 75%; }
  .space-line:nth-child(3) { width: 50%; }

  /* Quick Reference */
  .quick-ref {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 180px), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .quick-ref__item {
    padding: var(--space-4);
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .quick-ref__item h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }

  .quick-ref__value {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .quick-ref__color-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .quick-ref__color {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .quick-ref__item code {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  /* Theme-aware code display */
  .dark-value {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #09090b;
    color: #f4f4f5;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
  }

  .light-value {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #0f172a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Explore Links */
  .explore-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .explore-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-5);
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .explore-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    background-color: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  .explore-link:hover .explore-link__arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .explore-link__icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background-color: var(--accent-primary-muted);
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .explore-link__icon--typography {
    background-color: var(--accent-cool-muted);
    color: var(--accent-cool);
  }

  .explore-link__icon--components {
    background-color: var(--accent-violet-muted);
    color: var(--accent-violet);
  }

  .explore-link__content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .explore-link__label {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .explore-link__description {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .explore-link__arrow {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .brand-header__title {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
  }
</style>
